After these things you will design the nostrils and eyebrows, the mouth and ears, the hair, eyes, hands and arms, and the other shadows of the draperies, the footstools and feet, and you will raise them inside thus, with the smallest curved in- struments, above all taking care that it be not broken or per· forated.
